data.description: Don't miss this opportunity to live in Fairfield Beach! This 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home invites you in with a wrap around porch. Enter the home through the living room which leads to a bright, open kitchen. You'll also find a full bathroom on the main level. Upstairs, you will find the three bedrooms and another full bathroom. New flooring and fresh paint throughout. The one car detached garage is newly built.
